					"type": 23,
					"value": "Daisy AD when inside the Colony Tadpoling Centre. Daisy remarks on the occupants of the pods in the room (it is possible that all innocent occupants died before this point and there are only mind flayers in the pods). The Tadpoling Centre is where prisoners are transformed into mind flayers."
